\frac{p}{1-p}\frac{n-k}{k+1}\geq \frac{p}{1-p}\frac{n-(n+1)p+1}{(n+1)p}=\frac{p}{1-p}\frac{n(1-p)-p+1}{(n+1)p}=\frac{p(1-p)n+p(1-p)}{p(1-p)n}> 1
